        <h1>Burma: An Urgent Call for Prayer</h1>
        <p>There has been a request from inside Burma urging people of all faiths 
          to join in a prayer vigil for for the next three days. Inside Burma 
          they have asked that everyone pray in their doorways or just outside 
          their houses for 15 minutes at 8 pm Burma time on Sunday, Monday and 
          Tuesday, as sign of solidarity and an appeal for the restoration of 
          democracy in Burma. 
        <p>For those in the United Sates who would like to join in this, 8pm Burma 
          time is 6:30 am PST time and 9:30 am EST. 
        <p>If you cannot pray at this exact time please try to pray at anytime 
          that you can. 
        <p>Thank you and God bless you and God Bless the couragous people of Burma. 
